  {
    "id": "200662070448291_1600152068787065",
    "message": "The Spruce Tip Lager makes use of an old alternative for hops:  the new spring growth on evergreen trees.   Spruce tips were added during boil, whirlpool and during fermentation (dry-spruced!) for a citrusy tingle and a pine-y tang!  On tap today!  \n\nVisit Coshocton, Ohio! @visitcoshocton Ohio Craft Beer @ohiocraftbeer Northeast Ohio Craft Beverage News @neo_craft_brewery_news Cork & Tap Excursions",
